    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hello Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To combine multiple images into one image, you have to go to the top menubar and click on the  and select the  (right‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hello Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To combine multiple images into one image, you have to go to the top <strong><em>menubar</em></strong> and click on the <code class=\"language-text\">layer</code> and select the <code class=\"language-text\">merge layers</code> (<strong><em>right-click - Merge Down or Merge Layers</em></strong>).It will combine images.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you how I do combine images in photopea.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insert images.</li>\n<li>All select layer.</li>\n<li>Click on merge layer.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Insert image.</h3>\n<p>Open the photopea and Select photo, it will open a <strong><em>file</em></strong> browser or download folder you can select the image. And click <strong><em>open</em></strong> button.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/09fd1/image-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, image-1\"\n        title=\"Photopea, image-1\"\n        src=\"/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/828fb/image-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/ff44c/image-1.jpg 158w,\n/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/a6688/image-1.jpg 315w,\n/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/828fb/image-1.jpg 630w,\n/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/0ede0/image-1.jpg 945w,\n/static/05cf3f3864dad71c8bf9f3dd55c74920/09fd1/image-1.jpg 1208w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 2: All select layer.</h3>\n<p>There is a <strong><em>Layers panel</em></strong> onthe right side. Here, we can see all our layers. Click at the top one, press <strong><em>Shift</em></strong>, and click at the bottom one, to select them all.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/0c02e/select-layer.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, select-layer\"\n        title=\"Photopea, select-layer\"\n        src=\"/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/828fb/select-layer.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/ff44c/select-layer.jpg 158w,\n/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/a6688/select-layer.jpg 315w,\n/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/828fb/select-layer.jpg 630w,\n/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/0ede0/select-layer.jpg 945w,\n/static/5ed3bb5c7920cca2c9361454e9554e1e/0c02e/select-layer.jpg 1206w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 3: Click on merge layer.</h3>\n<p>To merge multiple images into one image, first select all layers in the <strong><em>layer panel</em></strong>, you have to go to the top <strong><em>menubar</em></strong> and click on the layer and select the <strong><em>merge layers</em></strong> (<strong><em>right-click - Merge Down or Merge Layers</em></strong>).</p>\n<p>You can merge layers after selecting them using the <strong><em>shortcut Ctrl + E (PC) or Cmd + E (Mac)</em></strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/00291/merge-layers.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.9620253164557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, merge-layers\"\n        title=\"Photopea, merge-layers\"\n        src=\"/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/828fb/merge-layers.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/ff44c/merge-layers.jpg 158w,\n/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/a6688/merge-layers.jpg 315w,\n/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/828fb/merge-layers.jpg 630w,\n/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/0ede0/merge-layers.jpg 945w,\n/static/2eb90dd11b55065b6988469ec1c1f6b3/00291/merge-layers.jpg 1209w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here we have combined images in one layer.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/902ab/final.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, final\"\n        title=\"Photopea, final\"\n        src=\"/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/828fb/final.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/ff44c/final.jpg 158w,\n/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/a6688/final.jpg 315w,\n/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/828fb/final.jpg 630w,\n/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/0ede0/final.jpg 945w,\n/static/1a9930864e64808d9e05edd93526b5f5/902ab/final.jpg 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>When you follow the above steps then it will combine images in photopea.</p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to combine images in photopea?","tags":["Photopea"],"date":"September 25, 2022","description":"Adding to combine images in photopea example with step by step guide - aGuidehub.","social_image":"media/template/photopea.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to crop only one layer in photopea?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-09-26-how-to